# Go conventions

- Module path and binary name: `bareai`
- Prefer stdlib; add deps only when they clearly earn their keep
- CLI: Cobra; TUI: Bubble Tea + Bubbles + Lip Gloss
- Errors: wrap with `%w`; user-facing messages via CLI layer, not deep collectors
- Collectors: context-aware (`context.Context`), bounded timeouts for HTTP/Docker
- No panic for expected missing tools (no Docker, no NVML, etc.)
- Support `--json` on inspect commands via shared encoder of `Snapshot` types
- Cross-compile friendly: gate OS-specific code with build tags (`//go:build linux`, etc.)
- Tests: table-driven unit tests for parsers/probes; integration tests optional behind tags
